templates.body:
Hi {{buyer_name}},

Receipt for your records:

- Order: {{order_id}}
- Date: {{date}}
- Item: {{item_title}}
- Total paid: {{amount}}
- Seller: Syndrax marketplace seller

Thanks for your purchase,
{{seller_signoff}}

Hi {{buyer_name}},

Thanks for order {{order_id}} ({{item_title}}).

This one is no longer available to ship. I've started the full refund/cancel so you're not stuck waiting.

{{similar_note}}

Sorry for the hassle,
{{seller_signoff}}

Hi {{buyer_name}},

Order {{order_id}} is going out in two shipments.

Shipped today: {{shipped_part}}
Tracking: {{tracking}}

Still coming: {{pending_part}}

I'll send the second tracking as soon as it drops. Sorry for the split — both pieces will get to you.

Thanks,
{{seller_signoff}}

Hi {{buyer_name}},

Order {{order_id}} is on the way.

Carrier: {{carrier}}
Tracking: {{tracking}}
ETA: {{eta}}

Track with the number above. If delivery day passes with no movement, reply here and I'll dig in.

Thanks,
{{seller_signoff}}
